content: I'm looking for some recommendations on new backpacks for my daily commute. I've been eyeing a few options online, but I want to make sure I get one that's comfortable and durable. Do you have any suggestions? By the way, on Fridays, I take a different route to work and it adds about 10-15 minutes to my commute - I take the bus down 3rd Avenue and walk the rest of the way to the office, which is a nice change of pace.
